ss="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border bottom"></div><div class="zm-noti7-popup-footer"><a href="/notifications" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-all zg-right">查看全部 &raquo;</a><a href="/settings/notification" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-set" title="通知设置" ><i class="zg-icon zg-icon-settings"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zu-global-notify" id="zh-global-message" style="display:none"><div class="zg-wrap"><div class="zu-global-nitify-inner"><a class="zu-global-notify-close" href="javascript:;" title="关闭" name="close">x</a><span class="zu-global-notify-icon"></span><span class="zu-global-notify-msg"></span></div></div></div><main class="pure-g receptacle"><section class="page-content-main pure-u-1 pure-u-md-17-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="module roundtable-profile clearfix"><a href="/roundtable/flower2018" class="photo visible-desktop"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0f536b9a3aff10e76f67e0c172357085_xl.jpg" srcset="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0f536b9a3aff10e76f67e0c172357085_b.jpg 2x" alt="春天去赏花" class="avatar"></a><div class="content"><div class="title"><h1><a href="/roundtable/flower2018">春天去赏花</a></h1><span class="status">已结束</span></div><div class="description">春天到了，生活在城市里的人类需要出去走走。植物为什么要开花？你的身边有哪些花卉植物？它们都叫什么名字，流传着哪些历史故事呢？本次圆桌，我们邀请了几位植物学和园艺的专业人士，来和大家一起聊一聊「花」。愿你走在春日的街头，你能辨认出遇见的那些花儿，了解更多它们背后的故事。</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="275" data-token="flower2018"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">11182598 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/flower2018/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="1470"> 1470</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li ><a href="/roundtable/flower2018">67 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/flower2018/questions">54 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/flower2018/comments">16 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose user-answers"><ul class="items" data-paging><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-81787362"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/20377325/answer/284453920"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="331283"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="20377325"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="81787362"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="284453920"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/20377325/answer/284453920">向日葵的种植方法是怎样的？有哪些要注意的地方？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>40</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">40</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/yuan-yi-shi-de-shi-jie" data-hovercard='p$t$yuan-yi-shi-de-shi-jie'>园艺师的世界</a>，<span title="和热爱园艺事业的人做朋友。" class="bio">和热爱园艺事业的人做朋友。</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="园艺师的世界" data-entry-url="/question/20377325/answer/284453920"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand"><b>（原创干货多图）</b>由于篇幅有限，我就抽一个景观向日葵着重介绍其栽培方法，按照惯例与图文相结合的模式把整个流程介绍简要介绍一下。景观向日葵属于易栽品种，可容器育苗 优点是开花整齐植株健壮，生长较快，但耗人工以及农资等成本；也可直播下地，省人工…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/20377325/answer/284453920">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="40"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/long-mao-mao-24" data-hovercard='p$t$long-mao-mao-24'>龙猫猫</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/athene-1-71" data-hovercard='p$t$athene-1-71'>阿焱</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/ke-ai-de-ni-79-62" data-hovercard='p$t$ke-ai-de-ni-79-62'>可爱的你</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p><b>（原创干货多图）</b>由于篇幅有限，我就抽一个景观向日葵着重介绍其栽培方法，按照惯例与图文相结合的模式把整个流程介绍简要介绍一下。</p><p>景观向日葵属于易栽品种，可容器育苗 优点是开花整齐植株健壮，生长较快，但耗人工以及农资等成本；也可直播下地，省人工以及农资成本，但因种子品质气候土壤等因素会出现开花不一致，甚至会出现未发芽死株等现象，生长前期根系弱，遇到高温天气还会死苗，所以我更倾向于种子容器育苗，但今年我们采用种子直播模式种植。</p><p>播种期要点:a,图纸规划品种场地清理；b,土壤深耕两次；c,向日葵目前与其他作物没有较明显连茬抗性，但土壤消毒还是有必要的；d,向日葵是喜肥作物所以基肥应当施足，有机肥肥料固体肥料以及粉末肥料均可；e,根据向日葵植株的大小种植间距在30cm—50cm不等，每穴两到三颗种子；f,由于向日葵发芽到开花需要50天到60天，所以播种期在八月上中期，天气炎热主要高温防晒，适当用无纺布遮盖。</p><p><br></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-68140413e2e824a2a184e6d2ef1a7759_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="565" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="565" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-68140413e2e824a2a184e6d2ef1a7759_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f314e9a7ca7b0bf28371a5b8b87bd718_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f314e9a7ca7b0bf28371a5b8b87bd718_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-de97e13287f0bf3995131fce9e15cde7_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-de97e13287f0bf3995131fce9e15cde7_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-780252b00e2dd96753b294e3c6ced3de_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-780252b00e2dd96753b294e3c6ced3de_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b1d8229dfd39e31dd4b0e4cc996d516_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b1d8229dfd39e31dd4b0e4cc996d516_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5a292cd70d84eb8cd8241b7cefc7029_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5a292cd70d84eb8cd8241b7cefc7029_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5acc088cc1e22a3656c65e4a5f3c4a96_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5acc088cc1e22a3656c65e4a5f3c4a96_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0704e8e1c5972d55408de5ad219d589_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0704e8e1c5972d55408de5ad219d589_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-66f895629bbd62d8039f141a210cf7d9_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-66f895629bbd62d8039f141a210cf7d9_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1033ca12e56a58ecb0745b2f9511bbfa_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1033ca12e56a58ecb0745b2f9511bbfa_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3d02644da90337fb52fdf5efbea8a07_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3d02644da90337fb52fdf5efbea8a07_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>生长期要点：a,注意防晒和高温；b,对于未发芽的植穴可在其他发芽两颗以上移栽补种；c,两片真叶以上方可移栽；d,植株弱的苗进行护盖防止暴晒致死；e,当植株15cm到20cm需要追肥，由于根系浅不建议挖穴埋肥，最好是浇水肥，15天到20天一次；f,注意防虫防病。</p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-43e0bc179cfbfb55be457f34a26dd781_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-43e0bc179cfbfb55be457f34a26dd781_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b291c5ad0f1d5965ca37df1ef646bd6d_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b291c5ad0f1d5965ca37df1ef646bd6d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ecb0026c033619702cf0b3f2470e1659_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ecb0026c033619702cf0b3f2470e1659_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-323968a84ac7e9a8da44f0d38ecce66f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-323968a84ac7e9a8da44f0d38ecce66f_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>盛开期要点：a,先花苞现蕾前期再打一次水肥，b,促使开花整齐长势旺盛；c,先花苞现蕾前建议打一到两次激素，例如矮壮素等可延长花期；d,向日葵花期在20天到30天，遇到阴雨天气花期会更短; e,注意大风天气，适时绑扎防止吹倒。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d24f5eac722918a25bf659ca5bdc1ca_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d24f5eac722918a25bf659ca5bdc1ca_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fb5a7a2829107a8961b34ead45c650b_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fb5a7a2829107a8961b34ead45c650b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6b28f440945618d6872284f52e767901_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6b28f440945618d6872284f52e767901_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0d62332ccacd00eba60ce2925786fda_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0d62332ccacd00eba60ce2925786fda_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2ff0f91454297d941f2a73efcb5f9004_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2ff0f91454297d941f2a73efcb5f9004_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ddfb53ad054b0382323e0b8092375f69_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ddfb53ad054b0382323e0b8092375f69_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2a18ae6f82c7f56a18894f6ccc1f6e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2a18ae6f82c7f56a18894f6ccc1f6e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7554853f905606d68cc7b7380420176c_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7554853f905606d68cc7b7380420176c_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>对于品种大家可能比较感兴趣，那就介绍一些吧</p><p>1,宝石红方</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c99724a047c895f6ca4d784e3ec3d939_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c99724a047c895f6ca4d784e3ec3d939_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2，出水芙蓉</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0d1507b0919fdf65f7fe1835894f5212_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0d1507b0919fdf65f7fe1835894f5212_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3，富阳</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-613540dbf8119c17e57e7f569ba287dd_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-613540dbf8119c17e57e7f569ba287dd_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-34f8f8bf2458f2570a2b34d4ab5ff79a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-34f8f8bf2458f2570a2b34d4ab5ff79a_r.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4，黑天鹅</p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d62d71f8d2fd35479be5f63b0d20a324_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d62d71f8d2fd35479be5f63b0d20a324_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2969d391100c384d5faad9c480404dd_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" cla