data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-da16f9f913f1e464506b418dd47c1f6d_r.jpg"></figure></b><b><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8e32c6fde1e5c25038780de41e666456_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8e32c6fde1e5c25038780de41e666456_r.jpg"></figure></b><b><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d0a0dbb037f105d8b7097a097162ad5e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d0a0dbb037f105d8b7097a097162ad5e_r.jpg"></figure></b><b><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3732f5fc21d5c4ed8b0034e49481491_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3732f5fc21d5c4ed8b0034e49481491_r.jpg"></figure></b><b><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-eea60a8c8c46802771a949b4d6a97048_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-eea60a8c8c46802771a949b4d6a97048_r.jpg"></figure></b><p><b>4，绿屏的藤本月季盛开（安吉拉等南阳月季）</b></p><p><br></p><b><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3171a01048f5a9692f358522f813036d_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3171a01048f5a9692f358522f813036d_r.jpg"></figure></b><b><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b1b7bf6c8bdcda09fe151e5bcb7b4029_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="ori