try answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>2</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">2</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/yuan-yi-shi-de-shi-jie" data-hovercard='p$t$yuan-yi-shi-de-shi-jie'>园艺师的世界</a>，<span title="和热爱园艺事业的人做朋友。" class="bio">和热爱园艺事业的人做朋友。</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="园艺师的世界" data-entry-url="/question/268624323/answer/346508299"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">改变形状：1、育种；2、温度过高过低、水分不足均会导致花的形状出现变化；3、冬季春化作用，低温不足会导致一些开花需要冬季春化作用的植物叶片变小，茎秆变细。改变色彩：1、育种；2、土质酸碱性；3、生长环境不良使植物变黄；<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/268624323/answer/346508299">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="2"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/gu-xing-ke-28-25" data-hovercard='p$t$gu-xing-ke-28-25'>喵大侠</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/bo-bo-89-43" data-hovercard='p$t$bo-bo-89-43'>波波</a></span></span> <span>赞同</span></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>改变形状：1、育种；2、温度过高过低、水分不足均会导致花的形状出现变化；3、冬季春化作用，低温不足会导致一些开花需要冬季春化作用的植物叶片变小，茎秆变细。</p><p>改变色彩：1、育种；2、土质酸碱性；3、生长环境不良使植物变黄；</p></script><a class="time" href="/question/268624323/answer/346508299">2018-03-20</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>2</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="21883255"><i cla